00:02:15.400 --> 00:02:16.680
No!

00:02:16.680 --> 00:02:18.000
Hear me out.

00:02:18.000 --> 00:02:20.480
They mean well. They’re here
to take us home.

00:02:20.480 --> 00:02:23.440
No more hiding in this forest
like fugitives.

00:02:23.880 --> 00:02:27.079
It’s true. Look at our faces.

00:02:27.079 --> 00:02:29.600
Do we look like the kind who’d enslave you?

00:02:32.800 --> 00:02:35.560
If you want to know how we’ll help you.

00:02:36.240 --> 00:02:38.160
I’ll tell you now.

00:02:53.079 --> 00:02:55.000
I believe every one of you.

00:02:55.000 --> 00:02:58.000
Loves freedom and wants
a life of your own.

00:02:58.400 --> 00:03:00.600
Not to be anyone’s property.

00:03:00.600 --> 00:03:02.920
Nor serve anyone else.

00:03:02.920 --> 00:03:05.160
And all who love freedom.

00:03:05.160 --> 00:03:07.560
Should live with dignity.

00:03:07.560 --> 00:03:10.560
And share equal rights.

00:03:11.360 --> 00:03:13.880
But the oppressive system.

00:03:13.920 --> 00:03:16.360
