00:03:18.680 --> 00:03:20.760
For generations to come?

00:03:26.320 --> 00:03:29.520
Now I have seized
the city of Singhanakhon.

00:03:30.240 --> 00:03:32.560
I want you all to go home.

00:03:32.560 --> 00:03:34.480
And join as one force.

00:03:34.600 --> 00:03:37.120
