Then tonight will be the last night
we stay here.

00:04:35.720 --> 00:04:37.960
Let’s have a farewell feast.

00:05:10.080 --> 00:05:12.520
Why sit alone, brother?

00:05:12.520 --> 00:05:14.400
Go dance with Worradej.

00:05:15.200 --> 00:05:16.520
