00:06:35.280 --> 00:06:36.880
Don’t blame me now.

00:06:38.600 --> 00:06:41.480
Your Majesty, please come dance.

00:07:01.320 --> 00:07:02.760
- What the,
- Kosol!

00:07:03.720 --> 00:07:05.000
Kosol!

00:07:05.720 --> 00:07:07.760
You can’t take Worradej away!

00:07:27.560 --> 00:07:29.400
Let me go!

00:07:29.400 --> 00:07:31.440
Let go! I said let go!

00:07:31.440 --> 00:07:33.080
Let go, ah!

00:07:34.000 --> 00:07:35.080
