to dance with you?

00:07:46.040 --> 00:07:48.040
So I brought you here
to dance with me.

00:07:48.960 --> 00:07:50.000
Hey.

00:07:50.000 --> 00:07:51.520
If you want to dance with me.

00:07:51.560 --> 00:07:54.000
Why drag me this deep
into the woods?

00:07:54.000 --> 00:07:56.360
Can’t you do things
like normal folks?

00:07:58.960 --> 00:08:00.360
I’m shy.

00:08:00.360 --> 00:08:01.680
I can’t dance.

00:08:01.920 --> 00:08:04.320
But if it’s swordplay,
I’m pretty good.

00:08:04.360 --> 00:08:05.960
When it comes to dancing.

00:08:06.040 --> 00:08:07.720
I’m hopeless.

00:08:07.960 --> 00:08:09.760
So I want you to teach me.

00:08:11.920 --> 00:08:14.400
Look, dancing’s just for fun.

00:08:14.400 --> 00:08:16.160
There’s no right or wrong.

00:08:16.160 --> 00:08:17.920
People dance to enjoy.

00:08:18.280 --> 00:08:19.680
Come on, Worradej.

00:08:20.680 --> 00:08:22.000
Teach me, please.

00:08:25.960 --> 00:08:27.680
