Like this, a lotus.

00:08:51.840 --> 00:08:53.880
Keep it graceful.

00:08:54.760 --> 00:08:56.080
Don’t bend your arm.

00:08:56.120 --> 00:08:58.120
Bend like this, yes, the hand.

00:08:58.200 --> 00:08:59.480
Okay.

00:08:59.480 --> 00:09:01.080
Now I’ll give the beat.

00:09:01.120 --> 00:09:04.320
It goes one, two, three, four.

00:09:04.320 --> 00:09:06.240
Then switch to the other side.

00:09:08.080 --> 00:09:09.800
Three, four.

00:09:09.800 --> 00:09:11.520
Uh-huh, try it.

00:09:11.520 --> 00:09:15.440
One, two, three, four.

00:09:15.800 --> 00:09:16.800
Okay?

00:09:16.840 --> 00:09:19.640
One, two, three, four.

00:09:19.640 --> 00:09:22.600
One, two, three, four.

00:10:00.880 --> 00:10:03.680
One, two, three, four.

00:10:03.720 --> 00:10:05.800
One, two, three, four.

00:10:05.840 --> 00:10:07.640
One, two, three,

00:10:07.640 --> 00:10:09.000
Don’t laugh at me.

00:10:09.480 --> 00:10:11.440
I just find you endearing.

00:10:11.440 --> 00:10:13.800
You’re dancing so stiffly.

00:10:13.800 --> 00:10:16.640
If it’s not your thing,
don’t force it.

00:10:17.600 --> 00:10:19.680
I’m forcing myself for you.

00:10:20.280 --> 00:10:22.160
Because I want
to dance with you.

00:10:22.880 --> 00:10:24.880
Like other lovers do.

00:10:25.400 --> 00:10:26.480
Then…

00:10:26.680 --> 00:10:28.960
If you want to dance with me.

00:10:28.960 --> 00:10:30.720
Shall we go back
to the village?

00:10:30.720 --> 00:10:31.880
Here.

00:10:32.000 --> 00:10:33.160
There’s no one around.

00:10:33.200 --> 00:10:36.080
It’s more fun with others,
and there’s no music. Come on.

00:10:40.640 --> 00:10:43.000
I want to be here with you,
just us two.

00:10:43.600 --> 00:10:45.680
We don’t need music.

00:10:48.480 --> 00:10:50.400
It’s already in my heart.

00:11:13.520 --> 00:11:14.840
I’m not jealous.

00:11:15.760 --> 00:11:17.160
Not jealous, but restless.

00:11:17.200 --> 00:11:19.880
Since Lord Kosol carried
my master away.

00:11:23.760 --> 00:11:25.280
No need to follow.

00:11:25.480 --> 00:11:27.080
He’ll be back soon.

00:11:29.360 --> 00:11:31.360
I wasn’t going to follow.

00:11:31.520 --> 00:11:34.200
I’m sure Worradej
will choose me anyway.

00:11:36.400 --> 00:11:38.200
That sure of yourself?

00:11:49.440 --> 00:11:51.600
This is way harder
than swordplay.

00:11:53.040 --> 00:11:54.200
Worradej.

00:11:54.520 --> 00:11:56.000
Don’t tell anyone.

00:11:56.000 --> 00:11:57.600
That I danced with you.

00:11:57.800 --> 00:11:59.920
I let only you see this side of me.

00:12:00.880 --> 00:12:02.480
Why not? Hey.

00:12:02.480 --> 00:12:03.960
You’re a warrior.

00:12:03.960 --> 00:12:06.400
But you can dance too,
it’s actually cute.

00:12:06.920 --> 00:12:08.280
Really cute?

00:12:08.680 --> 00:12:10.560
Of course. Cute.

00:12:12.480 --> 00:12:14.040
Then do you love me?

00:12:16.080 --> 00:12:17.720
What’s with you?

00:12:17.720 --> 00:12:19.560
How did it get to this?

00:12:21.800 --> 00:12:23.680
You’ve been dodging me all along.

00:12:23.680 --> 00:12:26.240
Every time I asked
how you feel about me.

00:12:27.720 --> 00:12:28.920
I don’t care.

00:12:29.120 --> 00:12:30.960
You must answer me today.

00:12:30.960 --> 00:12:33.960
If you don’t, I won’t let you
leave this forest.

00:12:33.960 --> 00:12:35.560
We’ll just stay here together.

00:12:37.240 --> 00:12:40.240
Hey, didn’t you say
you wanted to dance with me?

00:12:40.240 --> 00:12:42.760
So you tricked me
into a trap, huh?

00:12:43.480 --> 00:12:45.320
I don’t mind being in the woods.

00:12:45.320 --> 00:12:47.880
Plenty of ozone here, I like it.

00:12:50.360 --> 00:12:52.480
You’re dodging me again.

00:12:53.320 --> 00:12:55.720
But I think I can already guess
from your actions.

00:12:55.960 --> 00:12:57.680
What your answer really is.

00:12:58.800 --> 00:13:00.400
What we had before.

00:13:00.680 --> 00:13:02.800
Was only physical pleasure.

00:13:03.080 --> 00:13:04.840
Something you wanted from me.

00:13:05.760 --> 00:13:07.960
There was never any depth of heart.

00:13:08.880 --> 00:13:10.280
It’s my fault.

00:13:10.560 --> 00:13:12.440
For feeling it alone.

00:13:17.800 --> 00:13:19.040
Go back.

00:13:20.520 --> 00:13:22.960
And don’t toy with my heart again.

00:13:25.120 --> 00:13:26.920
Wait, Kosol!

00:13:28.200 --> 00:13:30.640
Give me a moment
to think of an answer.

00:13:31.480 --> 00:13:33.880
Oh man…

00:13:33.880 --> 00:13:35.520
Such a world-shaking problem.

00:13:35.520 --> 00:13:38.000
If only P’Oi and P’Chod were here.

00:13:38.000 --> 00:13:39.400
But right now.

00:13:39.400 --> 00:13:40.680
I’m all alone.

00:13:40.680 --> 00:13:41.720
So then.

00:13:41.760 --> 00:13:44.920
I’ll just be my own advisor first.

00:13:46.160 --> 00:13:48.040
What do you think, Worradej?

00:13:49.880 --> 00:13:51.480
This body belongs to me.

00:13:51.480 --> 00:13:53.480
So you should choose Banjong.

00:13:53.520 --> 00:13:55.160
Because I love Banjong.

00:13:55.160 --> 00:13:57.600
You should choose him
for my desire’s sake.

00:13:58.920 --> 00:14:00.040
But…

00:14:00.040 --> 00:14:02.000
You’re already dead, Worradej.

00:14:02.000 --> 00:14:04.400
I’m the one living
in this body now.

00:14:04.440 --> 00:14:05.840
That’s me.

00:14:05.840 --> 00:14:08.040
So I should choose Kosol.

00:14:08.080 --> 00:14:10.640
To follow my own desire,
that’d be right.

00:14:12.000 --> 00:14:13.440
And how do you know.

00:14:13.440 --> 00:14:15.440
That Kosol loves me.

00:14:15.480 --> 00:14:17.480
Or loves you, Prince?

00:14:17.800 --> 00:14:18.920
Exactly.

00:14:18.920 --> 00:14:20.840
If Kosol loves Worradej.

00:14:20.840 --> 00:14:22.840
Wouldn’t that be imposture?

00:14:22.880 --> 00:14:25.080
And that would mean.

00:14:25.080 --> 00:14:27.200
He doesn’t love us
for who we truly are.

00:14:27.200 --> 00:14:30.400
If we stay like this,
it won’t last.

00:14:30.440 --> 00:14:31.680
What should I do?

00:14:31.680 --> 00:14:35.600
Ugh, my head hurts.

00:14:44.800 --> 00:14:47.040
So now you can give me
an answer, right?

00:14:48.960 --> 00:14:50.160
Mm.

00:14:50.480 --> 00:14:52.720
But before I answer you.

00:14:52.720 --> 00:14:54.600
Let me ask you something.

00:14:55.400 --> 00:14:57.640
Earlier, you once said.

00:14:57.640 --> 00:14:58.920
That I.

00:14:58.920 --> 00:15:01.720
Before drinking poison
and after drinking it.

00:15:01.720 --> 00:15:03.720
Seemed like two different people.

00:15:04.680 --> 00:15:07.440
So which one do you love?

00:15:08.840 --> 00:15:10.280
Such a strange question.

00:15:10.480 --> 00:15:12.720
You talk as if you’re two people.

00:15:14.000 --> 00:15:15.320
To me.

00:15:15.600 --> 00:15:18.000
You’re still the same Worradej.

00:15:18.360 --> 00:15:20.800
The one with fierce determination.

00:15:21.680 --> 00:15:23.240
The only difference is.

00:15:23.240 --> 00:15:24.760
Back then you spoke less.

00:15:24.760 --> 00:15:26.840
Now you talk more, that’s all.

00:15:28.320 --> 00:15:30.000
That’s all, really?

00:15:30.400 --> 00:15:31.800
That’s all.

00:15:33.160 --> 00:15:34.440
So.

00:15:34.440 --> 00:15:36.240
Do you love the quiet one.

00:15:36.280 --> 00:15:38.280
Or the talkative one more?

00:15:44.000 --> 00:15:46.520
Whether it’s you back then,
quiet.

00:15:47.000 --> 00:15:48.680
Or you now.

00:15:48.680 --> 00:15:51.120
Made talkative by the poison.

00:15:52.200 --> 00:15:54.800
I believe inside
you’re still the same.

00:15:56.440 --> 00:15:58.320
Don’t worry, Worradej.

00:15:58.920 --> 00:16:01.040
Be whoever you are.

00:16:02.000 --> 00:16:04.080
Just be yourself, that’s enough.

00:16:04.920 --> 00:16:06.760
That’s the you I love.

00:16:15.080 --> 00:16:16.680
How lucky I am.

00:16:16.800 --> 00:16:18.320
That in this world.

00:16:18.320 --> 00:16:21.080
There’s someone who truly
loves my real self.

00:16:21.080 --> 00:16:23.480
And I love his true self too.

00:16:31.880 --> 00:16:33.320
Kosol.

00:16:35.880 --> 00:16:37.560
I love you.

00:16:46.120 --> 00:16:48.680
I’ve waited so long to hear this,
Worradej.

00:16:49.440 --> 00:16:50.960
I love you too.

00:16:51.600 --> 00:16:54.680
And I won’t give you the chance
to reject me again.

00:16:56.160 --> 00:16:57.800
What are you going to do?

00:17:08.480 --> 00:17:10.400
I’ll do this.

00:17:12.520 --> 00:17:14.599
Since tonight.

00:17:14.599 --> 00:17:16.960
Is already special.

00:17:17.960 --> 00:17:19.520
Let’s do something…

00:17:19.520 --> 00:17:21.839
That’ll make it unforgettable.

00:17:56.280 --> 00:17:58.720
It’s dark, walk carefully, sir.

00:17:58.840 --> 00:18:00.560
Watch out for wild beasts?

00:18:00.800 --> 00:18:03.720
Nothing’s scarier now
than Lord Kosol.

00:19:53.880 --> 00:19:55.520
Don’t you smile.

00:19:55.520 --> 00:19:57.680
I’m itching all over now.

00:19:57.680 --> 00:19:59.840
Got bitten on the butt by ants!

00:20:00.560 --> 00:20:01.920
And who was it.

00:20:01.920 --> 00:20:04.880
That said tonight would be
unforgettable?

00:20:05.080 --> 00:20:07.200
I’ll remember it till I die!

00:20:07.200 --> 00:20:09.160
I got stabbed by rocks too.

00:20:11.520 --> 00:20:12.920
So…

00:20:13.000 --> 00:20:14.720
Did you like it?

00:20:15.480 --> 00:20:16.640
I did.

00:20:17.400 --> 00:20:19.520
It’s like turning into
a wild beast.

00:20:19.880 --> 00:20:23.200
